1. Mobile Camera – Captures road images
2. ESP32 – Main controller and communication unit
3. Ultrasonic Sensor – Measures pothole depth
4. GPS Module – Provides exact location
5. YOLO AI Model – Detects potholes and cracks
6. Alert System – Sends notifications to users and authorities


#Flow

Mobile Camera
      ↓
ESP32
      ↓
YOLO AI Model
      ↓
Pothole / Crack Detection
      ↓
GPS + Ultrasonic Sensor
      ↓
Severity Classification
      ↓
Alert to User / Authorities



#If you are running YOLO on a laptop/cloud, then the architecture should be:Mobile Camera → ESP32 → Laptop/Server (YOLO AI Model)
                     ↘
          GPS Module + Ultrasonic Sensor
                         ↓
              Severity Analysis
                         ↓
                  Alert System

